        <hl1>Police Commissioner Has Prostate Cancer</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Just a week and a half after his boss, the mayor, made the same announcement, Police Commissioner Howard Safir said yesterday that he had prostate cancer. That two high-profile officials were told within days of each other that they had the disease illustrates the prevalence of prostate cancer, the second most common type of cancer in men.</p>
        <p>Article, Page B1.</p>
